    - -IP:/Github/VoxelEngine/engine_test/voxel_engine/dependencies/FastNoise2/include
    - -IP:/Github/VoxelEngine/engine_test/voxel_engine/dependencies/include
    - -IP:/Github/VoxelEngine/engine_test/voxel_engine/dependencies/glfw/include
    - -IP:/Github/VoxelEngine/engine_test/voxel_engine/dependencies/lwgl/include
    - -IP:/Github/VoxelEngine/engine_test/voxel_engine/dependencies/lwgl/dependencies/include
Documentation:
  CommentFormat: Doxygen